Rashied Staggie was once notorious for terrorising residents of Manenberg in Cape Town when he was the leader of the Hard Livings gang. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The family of Rashied Staggie has confirmed that his son Abdullah Taliep Boonzaaier was gunned down just hours after his father on Friday. The family says Boonzaaier was shot and killed in Mitchells Plain. UPDATE: Former Hard Livings boss Rashied Staggie shot dead The police have not yet confirmed the incident. Meanwhile, former Hard Livings gang leader, Staggie was shot and killed in Salt River, Cape Town earlier on Friday.